title: Ralph Cotton-Dead Man's Canyon
description: rThe Carly twins are identical - except one is good and the other is very bad. But when Blake guns down a sheriff, Abel runs with him because seeing his murderous brother lynched would be like watching himself hang. When Arizona ranger Sam Burrack closes in on the Carlys, after the shooting stops he finds Abel mourning his dead brother. But Burrack suspects that something is very wrong here
